Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.63,0:00:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 我就是这么从监狱里逃出来的\N{\fs38}Anyway, that's how I escaped from space prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.97,0:00:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 瘆人的地方\N{\fs38}Oh, scary place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.23,0:00:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 Rick 真是好一段故事啊\N{\fs38}Wow, Rick! That's... That's one... one heck of a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.80,0:00:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真希望我当时能在场目睹这一切\N{\fs38}I sure do wish I could have been there to see it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.15,0:00:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别扯淡了\N{\fs38}Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.75,0:00:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁会想看一个疯子科学家用自制黑科技武器\N{\fs38}Who wants to watch a mad scientist use handmade sci-fi tools
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:14.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撂倒精兵外星守卫的场面啊\N{\fs38}to take out highly trained alien guards
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.25,0:00:16.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如一家人在肖尼斯餐厅其乐融融\N{\fs38}when we can sit here and be a family at Shoney's?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.71,0:00:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 你能回来真是太好了 不管我们这是在哪儿\N{\fs38}Dad, it's great to have you back, no matter where we are,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.81,0:00:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你难道不想回家吗\N{\fs38}but wouldn't you like to go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.52,0:00:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感性地讲 宝贝女儿 肖尼斯餐厅就是我的家\N{\fs38}Emotionally speaking, honey, Shoney's is my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.72,0:00:24.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 但是你刚刚从监狱出来\N{\fs38}Yeah, but you just got out of prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.09,0:00:26.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这儿也不比那儿好得了多少\N{\fs38}I mean, how much of a step up from that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry 从卡座站起来 脱掉全身衣服\N{\fs38}Jerry, get out of the booth, take all your clothes off,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.36,0:00:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对折自己十二次\N{\fs38}and fold yourself 12 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.56,0:00:31.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听你的\N{\fs38}You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.27,0:00:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能对折六次是吧\N{\fs38}Six folds, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.73,0:00:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就把我关在一台9000系列析脑仪里吗\N{\fs38}W-W-What, have you guys got me in a Series 9000?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:42.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些贱胚虫子觉得我配不上你们最好的设备吗\N{\fs38}You cheap insect [bleep] didn't think I was worth your best equipment?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.11,0:00:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都跟那些管钱的说了\N{\fs38}Man, I told the money bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.54,0:00:47.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"你们都知道他是谁 对吧\N{\fs38}I said, "You know who this guy is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是想要我从银河里最聪明的哺乳动物那儿套情报\N{\fs38}You want me to get intel out of the smartest mammal in the galaxy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.68,0:00:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们最好给我配台先进的析脑仪"\N{\fs38}you better give me a decent brainalyzer."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.48,0:00:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是也点几个煎饼\N{\fs38}Well, you might as well order some pancakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.18,0:00:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不急着离开我脑里现在这个场景\N{\fs38}because I don't see the need to leave this part of my brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.42,0:00:57.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么不急呢\N{\fs38}Oh, I think you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.85,0:00:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟要么是你放松你的小脑\N{\fs38}Eventually, you're either gonna relax your cerebellum...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.31,0:01:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 放松我的肖尼斯  - 要么9000把你的脑子融掉\N{\fs38}- Shoney's. - or the Series 9000 is going to turn it into mush.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.88,0:01:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够放松了吗\N{\fs38}Relaxed enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.39,0:01:06.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我欣赏你 Rick\N{\fs38}I admire you, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.35,0:01:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我\N{\fs38}When I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.27,0:01:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick 听我说\N{\fs38}Rick, here's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.78,0:01:15.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进展怎么样\N{\fs38}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.40,0:01:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚不明朗 他好像臆现出了某种屁股\N{\fs38}It's hard to tell. He may have manifested some sort of butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.38,0:01:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还有这本事\N{\fs38}He can do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.81,0:01:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可是宇宙里最聪明的人\N{\fs38}He is the smartest man in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.92,0:01:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你们讲 银河联邦接管地球\N{\fs38}I tell ya, the Galactic Federation taking over Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.62,0:01:35.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我们家遇到过最好的事\N{\fs38}Best thing that's ever happened to this family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.62,0:01:37.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个星期我刚被提拔了第六次\N{\fs38}I just got my sixth promotion this week,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:38.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我都还不知道上班是干嘛\N{\fs38}and I still don't know what I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.76,0:01:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁在乎你被提拔得多高啊\N{\fs38}Who cares how high they promote you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.50,0:01:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给所有人发的工资都是药丸\N{\fs38}Everyone just gets paid in pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.03,0:01:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你不确定自己靠什么糊口时\N{\fs38}Well, when you're not sure what you do for a living,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.03,0:01:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,规矩就都由自己来定啦\N{\fs38}you can make your own rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.47,0:01:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Summer 对你爸爸尊敬点儿\N{\fs38}Summer, show your father some respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.67,0:01:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他挣的可是够六口人嚼的药丸呢\N{\fs38}He's pulling down a six-chewable figure income.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.34,0:01:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待会儿我来收拾 大家的药丸味道怎么样\N{\fs38}I'll get that in a moment. How are everyone's pills?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.11,0:01:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 Morty 你都没怎么吃你的药丸啊\N{\fs38}Oh, Morty, you've hardly touched your pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.11,0:01:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,午餐药丸吃的有点儿多 而且我\N{\fs38}I kind of had big pills for lunch, and I
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.15,0:01:59.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也不想吃药丸了\N{\fs38}wasn't gonna eat any more pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.52,0:02:01.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我谢你啊 Conroy\N{\fs38}Thank you, Conroy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.75,0:02:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会宠坏我们的 Conroy\N{\fs38}You'll spoil us, Conroy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.02,0:02:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这要是外公绝对忍不了\N{\fs38}Grandpa Rick wouldn't put up with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别提他的名字 他抛弃了我们\N{\fs38}Stop saying his name! He abandoned us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.69,0:02:09.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是Willem Dafoe!\N{\fs38}Willem Dafoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.22,0:02:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我今早想不起名字的就是这个人\N{\fs38}Th-That's the guy I couldn't think of this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.26,0:02:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别重蹈我的覆辙 Summer\N{\fs38}Don't make my mistake, Summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.76,0:02:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别神化弃你而去的人\N{\fs38}Don't deify the people that leave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的下场就是个马外科医生 活在外星人统治的世界\N{\fs38}You'll end up a horse surgeon in a world controlled by aliens
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.83,0:02:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而外星药物会让马儿们 永葆健康\N{\fs38}whose medicine keeps horses ... healthy forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.05,0:02:23.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在马比王八命还长\N{\fs38}Horses live longer than tortoises now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.81,0:02:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要沦落于此吗\N{\fs38}Is that what you want for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我要的只是在我大叫着跑掉的时候你还会在乎\N{\fs38}Maybe I just want you to care if I run away yelling!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有谁想吃药丸布蕾吗\N{\fs38}Who saved room for pill brûlée?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能理解你为什么选了这间家庭氛围的餐厅\N{\fs38}I can see why you chose this family-friendly restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.45,0:02:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来代表你的小脑\N{\fs38}to represent your cerebellum.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.02,0:02:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给人安全感 又舒适温馨 很有肖尼斯的感觉\N{\fs38}So safe, so comfortable, so Shoney's.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.25,0:02:41.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是承认吧 Rick 一直待在这儿你会疯掉的\N{\fs38}But admit it, Rick... you're going crazy cooped up in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.52,0:02:42.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去别的记忆里头逛逛吧\N{\fs38}Let's go visit some memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.86,0:02:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 想看特定的哪一个吗\N{\fs38}Oh, any particular ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.06,0:02:45.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想看我第一次勃起吗\N{\fs38}You want to see my first boner,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是要直接去看\N{\fs38}or should we go straight to the moment
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.61,0:02:49.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发现次元穿越方法的那一刻\N{\fs38}I discovered interdimensional travel?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.41,0:02:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧 你那下垂的两根在抽呢\N{\fs38}Ooh, your little flappy doodles are twitching.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是性奋了\N{\fs38}Does that mean you're aroused,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是你收到信号 有同伴找到了一串葡萄\N{\fs38}or did you just get a signal that one of your buddies found a grape?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是兴奋\N{\fs38}It's arousal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.20,0:02:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我很乐意去看看\N{\fs38}Yes, I'd like very much to visit
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:02:59.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你发明传送门枪的那段记忆\N{\fs38}the memory of you inventing your portal gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.37,0:03:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我的山芋很烫手啊\N{\fs38}Yeah, well, tough titties.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:04.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有比神经崩溃更烫手的山芋吗 Rick\N{\fs38}There's no tougher titty than a psychotic break, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.75,0:03:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 那就要看是哪个先崩溃了 我 还是 山芋\N{\fs38}Well, that depends on who breaks first... me or the titty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是某个你记忆里特别的人吗\N{\fs38}Someone special you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对她的记忆就排在这儿吗\N{\fs38}Is that your memory of her out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,排在911惊魂未定和最爱的球赛失利中间吗\N{\fs38}Between where you were on 9/11 and your favorite sports blooper?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:23.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们呆在这儿 你会死的 同所有的记忆一起死去\N{\fs38}If we stay here, you'll die, along with all your memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.33,0:03:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你带我去我想去的地方\N{\fs38}If you take me where I want to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.78,0:03:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也会在那儿 对吗\N{\fs38}she'll be there, too, won't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发明传送门枪的那天就是我失去她的那天\N{\fs38}The day I invented the portal gun is the day I lost her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:31.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 听起来不错啊\N{\fs38}Oh, that sounds cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:33.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能弄到我想要的 你也能道个别\N{\fs38}I can get what I want and you can say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.78,0:03:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 但是我来开车\N{\fs38}Fine, but I'm driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.51,0:03:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为剥去我们自由的借口\N{\fs38}As an excuse to strip away our freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是 你这是在干嘛\N{\fs38}Huh? What are you... What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.39,0:03:46.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外公肯定有秘密实验室 对吧\N{\fs38}Grandpa Rick must have some secret lab, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:48.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藏着镭射枪 飞行背包 还有太空坦克 \N{\fs38}With, like, laser guns and jets packs and a space tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.92,0:03:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我们可以去劫他出狱\N{\fs38}And we can go break him out of prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.53,0:03:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看这些死苍蝇\N{\fs38}Look at these dead flies!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.89,0:03:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能按照一定的顺序排列\N{\fs38}Maybe if we arrange them in a certain order,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.26,0:03:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会放一段全息图 或者打开一扇暗门\N{\fs38}it plays a hologram or it opens a secret door.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.10,0:03:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Summer 你吓着我了\N{\fs38}Summer, you're freaking me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.67,0:03:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道世界变了样 也知道你想念Rick了\N{\fs38}I know things have changed a lot, and I know you miss Rick,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是把他弄回来也不会有所好转\N{\fs38}but getting him back wouldn't make things better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.00,0:04:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 你知道吗 我们过得也不算糟糕\N{\fs38}And, you know, we're not doing so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.57,0:04:04.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过得糟糕透了 Morty\N{\fs38}We're miserable, Morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.07,0:04:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅强制宵禁 按他们奇怪的历法算起来我有47岁\N{\fs38}There's a mandatory curfew, their weird calendar made me 47,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:09.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃菲尔铁塔被变成了武器\N{\fs38}and they weaponized the Eiffel Tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得35岁挺好 我 我现在都可以租车了\N{\fs38}Hey, I like being 35. I-I can rent a car now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.78,0:04:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你就是个烂人\N{\fs38}Because you suck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外公被捕之后你就一言不发\N{\fs38}You've been keeping your lip zipped about it since Grandpa got arrested,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.68,0:04:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甩开了他你其实爽得不行\N{\fs38}but the fact is, you're freaking stoked to bail on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.21,0:04:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他甩开了所有人\N{\fs38}He bails on everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他甩开了当时还是个小孩的妈妈\N{\fs38}He bailed on Mom when she was a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.29,0:04:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他甩开了小小星球\N{\fs38}He... He bailed on tiny planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.03,0:04:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我以前没说清楚 Summer\N{\fs38}And in case I never made this clear to you, Summer,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:26.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也甩开了你\N{\fs38}he bailed on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.06,0:04:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他把你撇在一个被他毁了的世界里自生自灭\N{\fs38}He left you to rot in a world that he ruined
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.73,0:04:29.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他不在乎\N{\fs38}because he doesn't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:30.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他不在乎任何人 Summer\N{\fs38}Because nobody's special to him, Summer,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连他自己也不在乎\N{\fs38}not even himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你要是真想找回你的外公 拿把铁锹\N{\fs38}So, if you really want your grandpa back, grab a shovel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会让你失望的那个外公 就埋在你家后院里\N{\fs38}The one that won't let you down is buried in your backyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说对了\N{\fs38}You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.11,0:04:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 不是 我才没说对\N{\fs38}What?! No, I'm not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,激将法而已\N{\fs38}I-I was using ghoulish overkill!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.98,0:04:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,激将法 Summer\N{\fs38}Ghoulish overkill, Summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐 天呐\N{\fs38}Oh, God! Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.99,0:04:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这是去哪儿\N{\fs38}Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.26,0:04:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去所有一切开始的那天 也是终结的那天\N{\fs38}To the day it all began... and ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:58.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有事情转折的那一刻\N{\fs38}The moment that changed everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到麦当劳 请问您想点些什么\N{\fs38}Welcome to McDonald's. Can I take your order?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.80,0:05:05.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要10块麦乐鸡 多给点川香酱\N{\fs38}Yeah, I'd like to get a 10-piece McNugget and a bunch of the Szechuan sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能给多少酱就给多少酱\N{\fs38}Like, as much as you're allowed to give me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:09.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在1998年 麦当劳给迪士尼电影<花木兰>做宣传\N{\fs38}In 1998, they had this promotion for the Disney film "Mulan",
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时他们 当时他们\N{\fs38}where they... Where they...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.21,0:05:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们给麦乐鸡配制了一种新的蘸酱\N{\fs38}They created a new sauce for the McNuggets
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫做川香酱 超级好吃\N{\fs38}called Szechuan sauce, and it's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.44,0:05:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来他们就取消了 现在都没了\N{\fs38}And then they got rid of it, and now it's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.51,0:05:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有在记忆里\N{\fs38}This is the only place
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让我们尝到了\N{\fs38}we're gonna be able to try it, is in my memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.48,0:05:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick 你做这件事的同时你的大脑在融化\N{\fs38}Rick, you're doing this bit while your brain is melting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 好的 好的\N{\fs38}Okay. All right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 那个是  - 我\N{\fs38}- Is that...  - Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:30.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前穿蓝色裤子\N{\fs38}I used to wear blue pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.16,0:05:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么时候成功到达跨空间旅行的\N{\fs38}When'd you make the leap to interdimensional travel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有 是我做的\N{\fs38}I didn't. I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.05,0:05:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 哦 哦\N{\fs38}Well, well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是我们嘛\N{\fs38}If it isn't us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.24,0:05:45.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道发明传送技术最糟糕的一点是什么吗\N{\fs38}You know the worst part about inventing teleportation?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然间 你能够穿梭于整个银河\N{\fs38}Suddenly, you're able to travel the whole galaxy,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你发现的第一件事情就是\N{\fs38}and the first thing you learn is,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是最后一个发明了传输技术的人\N{\fs38}you're the last guy to invent teleportation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.71,0:05:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸运的是 你将发明一件更加厉害的东西\N{\fs38}Fortunately, you're about to invent something much more powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:55.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs38}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Summer 这事儿没必要让别人知道\N{\fs38}Summer, nobody has to know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以把它放回去 然后假装从来没看见过\N{\fs38}We could put it right back and pretend we never saw it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像我们也没见过老爸的塑料假人大腿一样\N{\fs38}like we did with Dad's mannequin leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:10.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 你留在这儿 我自己去救外公\N{\fs38}Fine, stay here. I'll rescue Grandpa myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.81,0:06:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你要怎么做  - 我还不知道 \N{\fs38}- And how are you gonna do that?  - I don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船到桥头自然直\N{\fs38}I'll make it up as I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:15.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外公不就是这样吗\N{\fs38}That's what Grandpa Rick does.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英雄不就是这样吗\N{\fs38}That's what heroes do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你想要看Rick是什么样的英雄吗\N{\fs38}Y-You want to see what a hero Rick is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我带你去个地方 Summer\N{\fs38}I-I'll bring you somewhere, Summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:22.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 嗯  - 我的天呐 孩子们\N{\fs38}- Um...  - My goodness, children.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放下那个非法机器\N{\fs38}Relinquish the illegal technology
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.45,0:06:27.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给最近的联邦议员\N{\fs38}to the nearest Federation representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我们来玩"胡言乱语"猜谜游戏\N{\fs38}And then we'll all play Balderdash.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.93,0:06:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 我的天呐\N{\fs38}Oh, my goodness! Oh, oh! My goo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 我的天呀\N{\fs38}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有一件一模一样的上衣\N{\fs38}I have that exact same top.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.21,0:06:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是哪里\N{\fs38}What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.65,0:06:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这个<饥饿游戏>版的Summer是怎么回事\N{\fs38}And what's with "Hunger Games" Summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的姐姐 这里原来是我的家\N{\fs38}That's my sister. This used to be my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想想看 任何事情你都能做到\N{\fs38}Imagine doing anything you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳到一个你从未到过的时间线\N{\fs38}then hopping to a timeline where you never did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去任何地点 任何时间\N{\fs38}Imagine going anywhere, anytime,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人能拦住你\N{\fs38}with nobody able to stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听起来挺孤单的\N{\fs38}Sounds lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:13.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孤单 老兄 你有你自己\N{\fs38}Lonely? Dude, you have yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.83,0:07:15.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无数个你自己\N{\fs38}Your infinite selves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一场永不散场的聚会\N{\fs38}It's a nonstop party
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.98,0:07:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的来宾都是我们唯一喜欢的那个人\N{\fs38}where all the guests are the only person we like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为做地球上最聪明的人是一件很酷的事情\N{\fs38}You think it's cool being the smartest man on Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是一旦我们给你这项技术\N{\fs38}but once we give you this technology,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就变成在每个可构想的世界里最聪明的人了\N{\fs38}you become the smartest thing in every conceivable universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无限的Rick 一个神\N{\fs38}The Infinite Rick, a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.91,0:07:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 算了\N{\fs38}Eh, pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.28,0:07:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 老兄 Rick们不会就这样算了的\N{\fs38}Excuse me? Bro, Ricks don't pass on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为你是谁\N{\fs38}Who do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个不一样的Rick 我猜\N{\fs38}A different kind of Rick, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.32,0:07:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 我们来看看这能持续多久\N{\fs38}Well, we'll see how long that lasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:41.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听到了挺科幻的声音\N{\fs38}I heard sci-fi noises.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有了进展吗\N{\fs38}Did you make a breakthrough?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.59,0:07:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点吧\N{\fs38}Sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我仔细地看了看自己\N{\fs38}I just took a long look at myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想科学这条路或许走不通\N{\fs38}and I don't think this science thing is gonna pay off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.93,0:07:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 为什么不带上Beth 然后一起出去吃冰淇淋呢\N{\fs38}Well, why don't I get Beth and we'll go out for ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.43,0:07:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dianne 那是在这间车库里面\N{\fs38}That, Dianne, is the last great idea
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.54,0:07:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会诞生的最后一个好主意了\N{\fs38}that will ever be had in this garage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:08:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这柯南伯格怪烤得挺好的\N{\fs38}Good roasted Cronenberg, I assume.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.84,0:08:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 你看起来 很野性\N{\fs38}Mom, you're looking... feral.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不敢相信Rick居然做了这种事情\N{\fs38}I can't believe Rick did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:09.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick的冒险里的这一部分\N{\fs38}These are the parts of Rick's adventures
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你见不到的 他抛下不管的那部分\N{\fs38}you don't get to see... The parts he leaves behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  谢谢款待\N{\fs38}All right, it's been great, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是来跑一趟 实地展示下"我就跟你说吧"\N{\fs38}I really only wanted to stop by here for a quick "I told ya so."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.99,0:08:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 所以 嗯  - 在找这个吗\N{\fs38}- So, uh...  - Looking for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.96,0:08:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拿着这个要干嘛\N{\fs38}What are you doing with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它有Rick的臭味\N{\fs38}It stinks of Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 为什么 为什么你要这么做\N{\fs38}No! Why?! Why would you do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.57,0:08:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你 你们这些人有什么毛病\N{\fs38}W-W-What is the matter with you people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你永远不能离开 她不能留下\N{\fs38}You can never leave. She cannot remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.80,0:08:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她有Rick的臭味\N{\fs38}She stinks of Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开枪 别开枪\N{\fs38}Hold your fire! Hold your fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.08,0:08:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是Morty C-137\N{\fs38}I'm Morty C-137.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:41.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们探测到一个被毁坏的传输枪 你的Rick哪去了\N{\fs38}We detected a compromised portal gun. Where is your Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:42.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 他被捕了  - Summer\N{\fs38}- He's in prison.  - Summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.72,0:08:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他被银河联邦抓住了\N{\fs38}He got captured by the Federation
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.39,0:08:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们打算去救他\N{\fs38}and we were going to rescue him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是令人烦恼 我们不能让大本营的秘密犯险\N{\fs38}Very troubling. We can't risk Citadel secrets
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.22,0:08:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,落入银河联邦的手中\N{\fs38}falling into the Federation's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.69,0:08:51.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们马上派Rick海豹突击队\N{\fs38}We'll dispatch S.E.A.L. Team Ricks immediately
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.79,0:08:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闯入关押C-137的监狱\N{\fs38}to break into the prison holding C-137.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 超帅  - 然后刺杀他\N{\fs38}- Boo-yah.  - And assassinate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超衰\N{\fs38}Boo-nah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 姑娘们 冰淇淋要化掉了\N{\fs38}Come on, girls! The ice cream's gonna melt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs38}Nooooooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.25,0:09:19.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇哦 这款酱真[哔]真赞\N{\fs38}Wow. This sauce is [bleep] amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.09,0:09:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了宣传一部电影是吗\N{\fs38}You said it was promoting a movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.05,0:09:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把3移象 再加2\N{\fs38}Carry the three, add a two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.59,0:09:29.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成了 [哔]成了\N{\fs38}I got it. I [beep] got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇哦 就 就是这个吗 传输枪\N{\fs38}Whoa. I-Is that it, the portal gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.92,0:09:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 就是那三行算术\N{\fs38}Yeah. That's the three lines of math
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.85,0:09:34.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分隔了我的人生\N{\fs38}that separates my life
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一边是生活中的人 一边是无知无觉的鬼魂\N{\fs38}as a man from my life as an unfeeling ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:38.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棒棒的\N{\fs38}Awesome-possum.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.23,0:09:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控制中心 你们拿到这个了吗\N{\fs38}Mission Control, you getting this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.67,0:09:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐 是的 是的 我们拿到了 是的\N{\fs38}Holy shit, yes! Yes, we got it! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 Rick 我会试着记住关掉析脑仪的\N{\fs38}Thanks, Rick. I'll try to remember to shut off the brainalyzer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.41,0:09:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实 我想它会自动关闭的\N{\fs38}Actually, I think it shuts off automatically
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你的大脑液化以后\N{\fs38}once your brain is liquid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:52.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道 也不在乎\N{\fs38}Don't know, don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我出去\N{\fs38}Pull me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.31,0:09:55.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 让我出去 你们能听到吗\N{\fs38}Hey, pull me out. Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.98,0:09:57.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 不 他们不能  - 为什么不能\N{\fs38}- Nope, they cannot.  - Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.85,0:09:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你刚刚上传的代码\N{\fs38}Because the code you just uploaded
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.07,0:10:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上并不是我的传送门枪公式\N{\fs38}wasn't actually my portal-gun formula,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.92,0:10:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是一个能让我完全控制析脑仪的病毒\N{\fs38}it was a virus giving me full control over the brainalyzer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.76,0:10:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么 这是一段记忆\N{\fs38}What are you talking about? This is a memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.52,0:10:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你不能更改记忆中的细节\N{\fs38}Y-You can't alter details of a memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.43,0:10:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 但是你可以改变任何东西\N{\fs38}True, but you can alter anything you want
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:12.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一个完全伪造的原创故事里\N{\fs38}about a totally fabricated origin story.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:14.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一个圈套 计划中止 我还在他的肖尼斯餐馆里\N{\fs38}It's a trap! Abort! I'm still in his Shoney's!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.77,0:10:16.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重复一遍 我们从来没有离开他的肖尼斯餐馆\N{\fs38}Repeat... we never left his Shoney's!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,计划完成 小伙子们 让我出去\N{\fs38}Mission accomplished, boys. Pull me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.04,0:10:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到\N{\fs38}Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.27,0:10:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 在我的大脑的剩余部分中尽情享受吧\N{\fs38}Okay, have fun in what's left of my brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将转去你的大脑中\N{\fs38}I'm gonna transfer to yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.84,0:10:24.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 没有足够空间容纳我的聪明才智\N{\fs38}Oh, there's not enough room for all my genius,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.84,0:10:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我给你留着我对柳条家具的恐惧\N{\fs38}so I'm leaving you with my fear of wicker furniture,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.88,0:10:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吹奏喇叭的渴望\N{\fs38}my desire to play the trumpet,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.38,0:10:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,买顶帽子的暂定计划\N{\fs38}my tentative plans to purchase a hat,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:31.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有六年的喜剧即兴表演研讨班\N{\fs38}and six years of improv workshops.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.55,0:10:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜剧成三(喜剧创作的准则)\N{\fs38}Comedy comes in threes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一个圈套 计划中止 我们从来没有离开他的\N{\fs38}It's a trap! Abort! We never left his...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:38.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs38}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照以前一样\N{\fs38}Another day, another dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.76,0:10:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是伟大的昆虫生物 不然呢\N{\fs38}Am I great insect creature or what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.36,0:10:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝贺你 特工\N{\fs38}Congratulations, Agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会因此大受赞扬的\N{\fs38}You'll be highly commended for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.17,0:10:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时刻等待着获许拥有成就感\N{\fs38}Always wait for permission to feel accomplishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.23,0:10:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我的座右铭  - 我还有一件事想不通\N{\fs38}- That's my motto.  - One thing still perplexes me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.64,0:10:53.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么Rick Sanchez会来自首\N{\fs38}Why would Rick Sanchez turn himself in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛 我只是个蠢虫子 但是Rick有可能早就知道\N{\fs38}Well, I'm just a dumb-ass bug, but it's possible Rick knew
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.91,0:10:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会被用这个装置审问\N{\fs38}he'd be interrogated at this facility,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.68,0:10:59.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而这个装置不仅有我们最想要的信息\N{\fs38}where we not only keep our most wanted,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.11,0:11:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还保存着我们最敏感的数据\N{\fs38}but our most sensitive data.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.41,0:11:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里任何拥有九级授权的人就可以\N{\fs38}Anyone here with level-nine access could
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.71,0:11:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不准 瓦解一个政府\N{\fs38}I don't know, collapse a government.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.45,0:11:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要去拉屎\N{\fs38}I'm just gonna go take a dump.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,介意我用一下九级的洗手间吗\N{\fs38}Is it cool if I use the level-nine bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.92,0:11:10.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九级核心授权密码是多少来着\N{\fs38}W-W-What's the level-nine master access code again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.36,0:11:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 简单 8 3\N{\fs38}Oh, that's easy... 8-3...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.89,0:11:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耶\N{\fs38}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.93,0:11:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是Rick海豹突击队\N{\fs38}S.E.A.L. Team Ricks in the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 Rick\N{\fs38}Hi, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 Rick\N{\fs38}Bye, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,D-99 你还好吗\N{\fs38}D-99, y-you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真扫兴 我还没来得及试用下虫屌呢\N{\fs38}I'm bummed. I didn't get to give that insect dick a test-drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 等等 等等 等等 我们受Rick委员会指示\N{\fs38}Wait, wait, wait, wait! T-The Council of Ricks sent us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.78,0:11:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们手里有你的Morty和Summer\N{\fs38}We have your Morty and Summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.98,0:11:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们作为俘虏关押在大本营\N{\fs38}They're prisoners on the Citadel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.48,0:11:36.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs38}Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,6755号房间安保系统破坏\N{\fs38}Security breach in room 6755.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:41.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下好了 不但我的计划被搞砸了\N{\fs38}Lovely. Not only is my plan screwed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于即兴表演的记忆也全没了\N{\fs38}I also forgot how to improvise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有安保人员\N{\fs38}All security people approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.02,0:11:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安保系统破坏\N{\fs38}Security breach.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.33,0:11:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一座全是外公的城市吗\N{\fs38}A city of Grandpas?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是Rick的大本营\N{\fs38}It's the Citadel of Ricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.64,0:11:58.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有来自不同时空的不同Rick\N{\fs38}All the different Ricks from all the different realities
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:12:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起聚在这里躲避政府\N{\fs38}got together to hide here from the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果政府每个Rick都痛恨政府\N{\fs38}But if every Rick hates the government,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.87,0:12:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么他们还会恨我们的外公\N{\fs38}why would they hate Grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.34,0:12:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为Rick最痛恨的是他们自己\N{\fs38}Because Ricks hate themselves the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:08.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我们的Rick是最典型的Rick\N{\fs38}And our Rick is the most... himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.05,0:12:09.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不是了 小屁孩\N{\fs38}Not anymore, homey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.35,0:12:10.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick海豹突击队把他的一字眉\N{\fs38}S.E.A.L. Team Ricks turned his unibrow
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.78,0:12:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分成了两根眉毛 用子弹分的\N{\fs38}into two brows... With a bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.49,0:12:17.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的Rick死了 你们的Rick死了\N{\fs38}Your Rick's dead! Your Rick's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.58,0:12:22.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官 Rick D-99 正单独返回\N{\fs38}Sir, Rick D-99 is returning from the mission alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.86,0:12:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很显然 Rick海豹突击队损失惨重\N{\fs38}Apparently, S.E.A.L. Team Ricks suffered heavy casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他进来\N{\fs38}Bring him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.65,0:12:30.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说他只愿意与一名更高级别的Rick通话\N{\fs38}He says he'll only talk to a Rick with higher clearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.07,0:12:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矫情 把那玩意儿给我\N{\fs38}La-di-da. Give me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.80,0:12:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,D-99 我是大本营自卫队的总司令\N{\fs38}D-99, this is the commander in chief of the Citadel's militia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.34,0:12:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很 很好\N{\fs38}Go... Good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.94,0:12:41.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个间谍 炸了他 我要去拉屎\N{\fs38}He's a spy. Blow him up. I'm gonna go take a shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.95,0:12:44.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,操作一支未注册的传送枪\N{\fs38}Operating an unregistered portal gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将一名Summer转变为激进分子\N{\fs38}radicalizing a Summer,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且与一个叛徒Rick合谋\N{\fs38}conspiring with a traitorous Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对此你如何辩护\N{\fs38}How do you plead?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.65,0:12:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么算得上是个公平的审判啊\N{\fs38}How is this a fair trial?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.09,0:12:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的辩护律师是个Morty\N{\fs38}O-Our lawyer is a Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.59,0:12:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不公平 你们没有权利 他也不是个律师\N{\fs38}It's not fair, you have no rights, and he's not a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.89,0:12:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们让他待在这里是因为他很逗\N{\fs38}We just keep him here because he's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.63,0:12:57.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧他那傻样\N{\fs38}Look at him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.03,0:12:58.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 耶\N{\fs38}Ha ha, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.16,0:13:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你与你的Rick断绝关系我们就从宽办案\N{\fs38}We'll be lenient if you renounce your Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.70,0:13:02.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说怎么样 Summer\N{\fs38}What say you, Summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我[哔]你的\N{\fs38}I say [bleep] you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:04.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外公是我的英雄\N{\fs38}My grandpa was my hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.94,0:13:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们杀了他是因为你们都嫉妒他\N{\fs38}You killed him because you were jealous of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.77,0:13:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点从发型就明显看得出\N{\fs38}That's pretty obvious from the haircuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.44,0:13:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你们把我怎么样都行 但是要放我弟弟走\N{\fs38}So do what you want to me, but let my brother go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.74,0:13:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经跟Rick断绝关系了\N{\fs38}He already renounced Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.38,0:13:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty\N{\fs38}Morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.55,0:13:14.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs38}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我才不要看你的游戏币收藏\N{\fs38}N-No, I don't want to see your Pog collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.58,0:13:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有与Rick断绝关系 我从来都没有\N{\fs38}I don't renounce Rick, and I never have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.95,0:13:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想保护我的姐姐\N{\fs38}I was just trying to protect my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.45,0:13:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想让你有正常的生活\N{\fs38}I wanted you to have a normal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.12,0:13:26.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是每次Rick出现时你就无法拥有的生活\N{\fs38}That's something you can't have when Rick shows up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.09,0:13:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有真实的东西变得虚假 所有正确的都变成错误\N{\fs38}Everything real turns fake. Everything right is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.89,0:13:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只知道你一无所知而他无所不知\N{\fs38}All you know is that you know nothing and he knows everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他虽然不是坏蛋 Summer\N{\fs38}And, well... well, he's not a villain, Summer,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.43,0:13:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他也不应该成为你的英雄\N{\fs38}but he shouldn't be your hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他更像是个魔鬼或者是个一塌糊涂的上帝\N{\fs38}He's more like a demon or a super [bleep]-up god.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.51,0:13:41.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们别[哔]这么深情地缅怀他\N{\fs38}Let's not suck the ghost of his [bleep] too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:43.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个恐怖分子 现在他死了\N{\fs38}He was a terrorist, and now he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.31,0:13:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 你以为我的Rick死了 其实他还活着\N{\fs38}Oh, yeah? If you think my Rick's dead, he's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要是觉得你们安全了 就等着他给你好看吧\N{\fs38}And if you think you're safe, he's coming for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:55.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 喔 喔 你来这里干什么\N{\fs38}Hey, whoa, whoa! What are you doing in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.25,0:13:58.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个区域只需要几个按钮和表盘\N{\fs38}This area's for teleporting the entire Citadel to somewhere else
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:14:00.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以把整个大本营传送到别处\N{\fs38}using only buttons and dials.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.39,0:14:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这个设计\N{\fs38}Yeah, well, it's a bad idea
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.03,0:14:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就很不明智了对不对\N{\fs38}to have it designed that way then, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.38,0:14:11.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这[哔]是怎么搞的\N{\fs38}What the [bleep]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.94,0:14:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们被传送到了银河联邦监狱\N{\fs38}We just teleported into a galactic federal prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.51,0:14:17.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去拉屎\N{\fs38}I'm gonna go take a shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.01,0:14:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法庭内请保持肃静\N{\fs38}Order in the court!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.44,0:14:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 这是怎么回事 我的天哪\N{\fs38}Whoa! What the hell?! Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 等等 等等 等等 不 不 不\N{\fs38}Wait, wait, wait, wait! No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.35,0:14:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔\N{\fs38}Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.42,0:14:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔\N{\fs38}Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.53,0:14:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大本营被传送到了联邦的地盘\N{\fs38}The Citadel's been teleported to Federation space.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完蛋了 这一定是C-137干的\N{\fs38}It's doomed. This has to be C-137, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:47.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我们该怎么办  - 他要找我们算账了\N{\fs38}- What are we gonna do?! - You know he's coming for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.94,0:14:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 都冷静 我们可以把他的Summer当做人质\N{\fs38}All right, calm down! We have his Summer as a hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.18,0:14:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很显然 我抓住她了\N{\fs38}Obviously, I get her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.31,0:14:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们用"瑞克 激光 剪刀"决定谁抓住Morty\N{\fs38}You guys play Rick, Laser, Scissors for the Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.35,0:14:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是出的什么\N{\fs38}W-W-What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.92,0:14:58.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报复\N{\fs38}Payback.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.02,0:15:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外公\N{\fs38}Grandpa Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:04.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 还用说吗  - 你还活着\N{\fs38}- Duh! - You're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.16,0:15:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Rick  - Morty 拿着这个 待会儿用得上\N{\fs38}- Rick! - Morty, take this. You're gonna need it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 等等 喔\N{\fs38}Hold on, hold on. Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.45,0:15:14.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了 Rick\N{\fs38}That's enough, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:16.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是想干什么\N{\fs38}What... What's this supposed to accomplish?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的外孙多得用不完\N{\fs38}We have infinite grandkids.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.51,0:15:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这好比是想在凯撒宫酒店里花掉迪士尼代币\N{\fs38}You're trying to use Disney bucks at a Caesar's Palace here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.48,0:15:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在唬你 他很爱我的\N{\fs38}That's a bluff. He's bluffing, sir. He loves me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.67,0:15:25.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不按套路出牌 不理性又感情用事\N{\fs38}You're a rogue Rick... Irrational, passionate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.21,0:15:27.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爱你的外孙 你来这儿就是要救他们\N{\fs38}You love your grandkids. You came to rescue them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.91,0:15:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是来杀你的 哥们\N{\fs38}I came to kill you, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.75,0:15:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都不是我原装的Summer\N{\fs38}That's not even my original Summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:33.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈呀 他不是在唬人\N{\fs38}Oh, my God. He's not bluffing. He's not bluffing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.12,0:15:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Rick - 干嘛不直接射穿她\N{\fs38}- Rick? - Why not shoot through her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.09,0:15:37.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,20码的距离 9口径脉冲手枪\N{\fs38}20 yards, nine-gauge plasma pistol,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.36,0:15:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的第一枪会液化她的内脏 但只能打伤你\N{\fs38}My first shot would liquify her insides and injure you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二枪后坐力会增加\N{\fs38}second shot adds recoil.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我等你枪毙她 我的风险就会降到最低\N{\fs38}The risk to me is minimized if I wait for you to shoot her,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.66,0:15:45.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就希望你这么做\N{\fs38}which I'm encouraging you to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.06,0:15:46.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 搞什么[哔]啊  - 或者放了她\N{\fs38}- What the [beep] - Or let her go,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我就可以让你死得痛快些\N{\fs38}which I will reward with a quicker death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你爱她\N{\fs38}Because you love her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:52.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你才能让我给你最利索的一枪\N{\fs38}Because it's incentive for you to give me my cleanest shot,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.74,0:15:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死得不那么痛苦\N{\fs38}which will be your least painful death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果你想要死得慢些 我也很有兴趣陪你玩\N{\fs38}But if you want to die slower than that, I'm super into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,0:15:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想这么做的话你只需要杀了那个女孩\N{\fs38}All you got to do to get that started is kill the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.91,0:16:01.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我恨你  - 我才不在乎 亲爱的\N{\fs38}- I hate you! - Not an issue, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:03.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了 把枪放下 Rick\N{\fs38}That's enough! Drop the gun, Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:05.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 我知道你太蠢了 不懂我在干嘛\N{\fs38}Morty, I know you're too stupid to get this,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:06.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你现在真[哔]是在捣乱\N{\fs38}but you're really [bleep] this up right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:09.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能让你害死我姐姐 把枪放下\N{\fs38}I'm not letting you let my sister die! Drop the gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.22,0:16:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没想让她死 你[哔]智障\N{\fs38}I wasn't gonna let her die, you [bleep] moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.22,0:16:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 哈  - 噢\N{\fs38}- Ha! - Aww.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.39,0:16:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关键是让他以为我打算这么做\N{\fs38}The point is he thought I was going to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便说一句 我确实被你骗到了\N{\fs38}I totally did, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.46,0:16:16.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你[哔]个智障 Morty\N{\fs38}You're a [bleep] moron, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.93,0:16:18.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 你[哔]傻逼\N{\fs38}Morty, you [bleep] idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.23,0:16:19.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真[哔]是个傻逼 Morty\N{\fs38}You're a serious [bleep] idiot, Morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.93,0:16:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这等于是害死了我们所有人\N{\fs38}You basically killed us all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你太烂了  - 你傻得和一袋沙子没啥区别\N{\fs38}- You're the worst! - You're as dumb as a bag of sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.04,0:16:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看现在到底是谁傻\N{\fs38}Who's stupid now, bitch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.68,0:16:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 他才刚回到我们身边\N{\fs38}Morty, we just got him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得漂亮啊 Morty\N{\fs38}That was amazing, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:36.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天啊 你可真棒\N{\fs38}Oh, my God. Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 现在我们来做个了结\N{\fs38}Okay, let's wrap this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.78,0:16:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好 Morty 我们走吧 孩子们\N{\fs38}Good job, Morty. Let's go, kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥 刚才是怎么回事\N{\fs38}What?! What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是我的老把戏罢了\N{\fs38}Oldest Rick trick in the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.28,0:16:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"枪是假的 对峙下对我开枪"\N{\fs38}"Fake gun, shoot me in standoff."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.51,0:16:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 太机智啦  - 哈 没错\N{\fs38}- Brilliant. - Ha, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.99,0:16:50.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好我看见字条了\N{\fs38}G-Good thing I saw that note.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.11,0:16:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就不能直接传送回家吗\N{\fs38}Can't we just portal home?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.31,0:17:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我收拾好我搞出来的烂摊子再说\N{\fs38}Not until I finish what I started.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.31,0:17:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是不用密码就能获得九级权限的办法\N{\fs38}And that is how you get level-nine access without a password.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.31,0:17:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动\N{\fs38}Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.48,0:17:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这枪给月度最佳员工 女士们先生们\N{\fs38}Employee of the month, ladies and gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.35,0:17:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你到底要用九级权限做什么\N{\fs38}So, what are you doing with level-nine access anyways?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.45,0:17:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 毁掉银河联邦啊  - 棒极了  - 哇 太酷了\N{\fs38}- Destroying the galactic government. - Awesome! - Whoa, cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.25,0:17:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是要让他们用核武器自相残杀吗\N{\fs38}Are you going to set all their nukes to target each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.32,0:17:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 还可以重新设定他们军队的传送门\N{\fs38}Ooh, or... or reprogram their military portals
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.12,0:17:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来毁掉他们所有的太空舰队\N{\fs38}to disintegrate their entire space fleet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.79,0:17:20.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好主意 孩子们 快要为你们骄傲了\N{\fs38}Good pitches, kids. I'm almost proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.83,0:17:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你们看仔细点 外公马上要摧毁一个帝国了\N{\fs38}But watch closely as Grandpa topples an empire
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.13,0:17:26.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要把这个1改成0\N{\fs38}by changing a one... to a zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.27,0:17:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生 咱们货币刚刚跌到一文不值了\N{\fs38}Mr. President, the Blemflarck's value just dropped to nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.87,0:17:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 什么意思  - 我是说\N{\fs38}- What do you mean? - I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银河联邦的唯一货币\N{\fs38}our single centralized galactic currency
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.21,0:17:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚还一块钱值一块钱 现在一块钱的价值是零\N{\fs38}just went from being worth one of itself to zero of itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点 同志们\N{\fs38}Calm down, people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.88,0:17:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,启用银河联邦自卫队 颁布戒严令\N{\fs38}Deploy the galactic militia and declare martial law.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官 遵命\N{\fs38}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.98,0:17:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我们用什么付他们工资啊\N{\fs38}Uh, what should I pay them with?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.78,0:17:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为国家效劳的荣耀就是他们的报酬\N{\fs38}Their payment is the honor they'll feel to serve their...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.85,0:17:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 我凭啥对他大喊大叫 谁付我钱啊\N{\fs38}Wait. Who's paying me to yell at this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.02,0:17:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能回答 如果给我钱的话\N{\fs38}I can answer that... For money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没想到我还能看到这么一幕\N{\fs38}I never thought I'd live to see this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.96,0:17:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同志们 同志们 别吵了\N{\fs38}Gentlemen, gentlemen, gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.33,0:17:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实还有个你们没想到的方法\N{\fs38}There's a solution here you're not seeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.20,0:18:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 把你的夹克给我  - 快把裤子扒下来给我\N{\fs38}- Give me your jacket! - Give me those pants!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在没有贫富之分了\N{\fs38}There's no rich people or poor people!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.04,0:18:13.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要更多夹克\N{\fs38}I want more jackets!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得最多裤子者得天下\N{\fs38}He who controls the pants controls the galaxy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.56,0:18:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决不给虫族再次统治地表世界的机会\N{\fs38}No longer will the insects have domain over surface world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.77,0:18:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry 到底发生什么了啊\N{\fs38}Jerry, what the hell is happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.91,0:18:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银河联邦垮台了\N{\fs38}The galactic government collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.78,0:18:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\fs38}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.65,0:18:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 虽然说出来并不光彩 但是\N{\fs38}Look, I-I'm not proud to share this, but the truth is,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.61,0:18:51.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚才一路爬回来的 这招真管用\N{\fs38}I just kept crawling, and it kept working.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.85,0:18:53.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事就太好了\N{\fs38}Oh, I'm glad you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.65,0:18:55.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一直纵容你爸爸\N{\fs38}Are we ever going to stop paying for
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.95,0:18:57.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是就要一直为此付出代价\N{\fs38}indulging your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.72,0:19:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经失去了孩子 地球 和工作\N{\fs38}Our children, our planet, our jobs?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我们还拥有什么呢\N{\fs38}Is there anything left to lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.09,0:19:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩彼此了 而且我永远不会离开你的\N{\fs38}Just each other, and I'll never let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.46,0:19:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起我做了这些事\N{\fs38}And I'm so sorry I ever did this to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.13,0:19:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猜猜是谁把政府搞垮了\N{\fs38}Guess who dismantled the government?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.44,0:19:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 求求你别再离开我了  - 再也不会了 宝贝\N{\fs38}- Please don't leave me again. - I never will, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.40,0:19:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是对的 他是故意自首的\N{\fs38}I was right. He turned himself in on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.37,0:19:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都在他的计划之中\N{\fs38}It was all part of his plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.77,0:19:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry 还有淡啤酒吗\N{\fs38}Jerry, is there any light beer left?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本想不到你在监狱里会想念什么\N{\fs38}It's insane what you miss in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.11,0:19:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 没有\N{\fs38}Um... okay. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.11,0:19:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不 没有 很明确地告诉你\N{\fs38}No, no, no. Foot down time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 你是对的 有伏特加吗\N{\fs38}No, you're right. Where's the vodka?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.82,0:19:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Beth你来选吧 有他没我 有我没他\N{\fs38}Beth, it's him or me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来你们需要单独谈谈\N{\fs38}Seems like you guys need some privacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我还是去车库吧\N{\fs38}I'll, uh... I'll be in the garage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么[哔]啊 Jerry\N{\fs38}What the [bleep]! Not cool, Jerry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.67,0:19:44.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车库是男人的城堡\N{\fs38}A man's garage is his castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.11,0:19:51.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry会\N{\fs38}Jerry's going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.81,0:19:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花一些时间\N{\fs38}spend some time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回归单身了\N{\fs38}divorced.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.15,0:19:56.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 那太遗憾了 宝贝\N{\fs38}Oh, I-I'm sorry to hear that, sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.85,0:19:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个决定不是因为我吧\N{\fs38}I hope I had nothing to do with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.25,0:20:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 天啊 爸爸 别想太多 和你没什么关系\N{\fs38}Oh, God, Dad, that is not your burden to bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.02,0:20:03.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉很内疚 把你想得这么坏\N{\fs38}I feel terrible that I misjudged you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.86,0:20:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样对Jerry也好\N{\fs38}This is gonna be good for Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.66,0:20:07.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 对所有人都好  - 对所有人都好\N{\fs38}- For everybody. - For everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.55,0:20:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最好去看看他\N{\fs38}I better tend to Jerry
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.76,0:20:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以免他改变主意 不想搬出去了\N{\fs38}before he changes his mind and doesn't move out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.40,0:20:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不打扰你们两个的小冒险了\N{\fs38}I will leave you two to your adventures.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.77,0:20:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老天爷 Nancy说\N{\fs38}Oh, my God. Nancy says
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.47,0:20:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们正在学校操场里对那些外星人用刑\N{\fs38}they're drawing and quartering aliens in the school courtyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.97,0:20:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且这算是爱国行为\N{\fs38}and it technically counts as patriotism.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.27,0:20:25.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊 我的父母真的要离婚吗\N{\fs38}Geez! Are my parents seriously gonna get divorced?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.21,0:20:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 Rick 我要去\N{\fs38}All right, Rick, I'm gonna go to my...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.65,0:20:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪也别去 Morty 你听见你妈妈说的了\N{\fs38}Not so fast, Morty. You heard your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.48,0:20:31.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还要去一起冒险呢 Morty 就你和我\N{\fs38}We've got adventures to go on, Morty... just you and me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.05,0:20:33.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时带上你姐姐 或者你妈妈\N{\fs38}And sometimes your sister and sometimes your mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但绝不带你爸爸\N{\fs38}but never your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.11,0:20:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想知道原因吗 Morty 因为他惹恼我了\N{\fs38}You want to know why, Morty? Because he crossed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.12,0:20:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等会儿 Rick 这有点黑暗\N{\fs38}Okay, take it easy, Rick. T-T-That's dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 还会更黑暗的 Morty\N{\fs38}Oh, it gets darker, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到冒险中最黑暗的时刻\N{\fs38}Welcome to the darkest year of our adventures.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.39,0:20:43.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 第一个改变 你爸爸出局了  - 哦 天啊\N{\fs38}- First thing that's different... no more Dad, Morty. - Oh, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:45.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他威胁说要把我交给政府\N{\fs38}He threatened to turn me in to the government,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.46,0:20:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我设计让他和政府都滚蛋了\N{\fs38}so I made him and the government go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.53,0:20:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么[哔]\N{\fs38}Oh [beep].
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.48,0:20:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经替代了他\N{\fs38}I've replaced them both
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你家和这个宇宙都是我做主\N{\fs38}as the de facto patriarch of your family and your universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.90,0:20:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 如果我不带着你和你姐姐回家  - 哦天\N{\fs38}- Your mom wouldn't have accepted me if I came home... - Oh, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.68,0:20:55.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妈妈就不会接受我\N{\fs38}Without you and your sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.75,0:20:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 所以你现在知道我救你们的真正原因了  - 噢\N{\fs38}- so now you know the real reason I rescued you. - Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.68,0:20:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚刚掌控了整个家 Morty 如果你向你妈妈\N{\fs38}I just took over the family, Morty, and if you tell your mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.78,0:21:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 不会吧  - 或者你姐姐告密 我绝不承认\N{\fs38}- Oh, man. - ...or sister I said any of this, I'll deny it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.65,0:21:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 他们会相信我 因为我是英雄 Morty  - 你不会承认\N{\fs38}- ...and they'll take my side because I'm a hero, Morty. - You're gonna deny it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你不得不\N{\fs38}And now you're gonna have to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖按我说的做了 Morty 永远\N{\fs38}And do whatever I say, Morty, forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.62,0:21:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我要出去 再找点那个\N{\fs38}And I'll... I'll go out and I'll find some more of that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.52,0:21:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了<花木兰>电影推出的川香酱了 Morty\N{\fs38}"Mulan" Szechuan teriyaki dipping sauce, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊\N{\fs38}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.44,0:21:14.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为一切都是为了川香酱 Morty\N{\fs38}Because that's that's what this is all about, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.03,0:21:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 川香酱  - 那才是一切\N{\fs38}- Szechuan? - That's my one-armed man!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.63,0:21:17.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不是为了给死去的妻女复仇 Morty\N{\fs38}I'm not driven by avenging my dead family, Morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.76,0:21:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是假的\N{\fs38}That was fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.35,0:21:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都是为了麦乐鸡的蘸酱\N{\fs38}I-I-I'm driven by finding that McNugget sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.60,0:21:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 麦乐鸡  - 我要吃那个<花木兰>的麦乐鸡蘸酱 Morty\N{\fs38}- McNuggets? - I want that "Mulan" McNugget sauce, Morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.90,0:21:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 这才是串起一切的主线 Morty  - 你在胡说什么\N{\fs38}- That's my series arc, Morty. - What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.20,0:21:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这个要拍九季\N{\fs38}If it takes nine seasons,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.48,0:21:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要找到这个麦乐鸡蘸酱\N{\fs38}I want my McNugget dipping sauce,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.08,0:21:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 川香酱 Morty  - 你到底在胡言乱语些什么\N{\fs38}- Szechuan sauce, Morty. - What are you talking about, Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.68,0:21:30.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个蘸酱会一路支持我们到最后\N{\fs38}That's what's gonna take us all the way to the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.29,0:21:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Morty  - 你在说什么啊\N{\fs38}- Morty. - What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:32.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有九季 Morty\N{\fs38}Season... Nine more seasons, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:35.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有九季我才能找到那个四川蘸酱\N{\fs38}Nine more seasons until I get that dipping Szechuan sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.11,0:21:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 那是什么啊  - 也就是还要97年 Morty\N{\fs38}- What is that?! - For 97 more years, Morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.08,0:21:38.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊到底\N{\fs38}What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.28,0:21:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说我要那个麦乐鸡的蘸酱 Morty\N{\fs38}I want that McNugget sauce, Morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.15,0:22:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了吗\N{\fs38}Is it ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.35,0:22:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 现在就可以让它上线\N{\fs38}Yes. We can bring it online now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.25,0:22:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\fs38}Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.66,0:22:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是凤凰人\N{\fs38}I am Phoenix Person.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.43,0:22:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凤凰人 这是我们决定好的名字吗\N{\fs38}Phoenix Person? Is that what we settled on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.47,0:22:29.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为我们说好的是赛博鸟\N{\fs38}I thought we all agreed on Cyber Bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.47,0:22:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说你不在意他叫什么名字的\N{\fs38}You said you didn't care what he was called
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.17,0:22:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我们把他救回来就行\N{\fs38}as long as we brought him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.70,0:22:34.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这么说的 但是凤凰男也太不像话了吧\N{\fs38}Yeah, but Phoenix Person?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.17,0:22:35.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 随他去吧 随便了\N{\fs38}Fine, [beep] it. Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.01,0:22:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起飞\N{\fs38}Ka-kaw!
